1
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:11,200
[My Uncanny Destiny]

2
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,190
♫ Listening to the wind blow while watching clouds sway ♫

3
00:00:19,190 --> 00:00:23,290
♫ The moon hangs on treetops and links the romantic Magpie Bridge ♫

4
00:00:23,290 --> 00:00:27,820
♫ You liven up everything ♫

5
00:00:27,820 --> 00:00:33,000
♫ Why, why did fate let us meet? ♫

6
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:39,580
♫ My Lord, things are looking bad ♫

7
00:00:39,580 --> 00:00:43,580
♫ She has forgotten all about the past ♫

8
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:45,680
♫ The Milky Way is far distant ♫

9
00:00:45,680 --> 00:00:49,280
♫ That day, by some mistake ♫

10
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:51,920
♫ You landed in my arms ♫

11
00:00:51,920 --> 00:00:55,850
♫ My Lord, things are looking bad ♫

12
00:00:55,850 --> 00:00:59,930
♫ Why do I smile when I see her? ♫

13
00:00:59,930 --> 00:01:02,030
♫ It's unpredictable ♫

14
00:01:02,030 --> 00:01:08,090
♫ I want to stay with you till the end of the world ♫

15
00:01:08,090 --> 00:01:11,390
♫ Oh, only then I realized ♫

16
00:01:11,390 --> 00:01:16,700
♫ You tugged at my heartstrings ♫

17
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:19,700
♫ Look at that boundless longing ♫

18
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:24,400
♫ Daily, little by little, it spreads in the world ♫

19
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:28,300
♫ Listening to the wind blow while watching clouds sway ♫

20
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:32,500
♫ The moon hangs on treetops and links the romantic Magpie Bridge ♫

21
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:37,040
♫ You liven up everything ♫

22
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:40,690
♫ Why, why did we have to meet? ♫

23
00:01:40,690 --> 00:01:44,730
♫ Listen to my heart beat and see your eyes drift ♫

24
00:01:44,730 --> 00:01:48,730
♫ I hold your hand and fall for your gentleness ♫

25
00:01:48,730 --> 00:01:53,330
♫ Is Cupid to blame for making a mistake? ♫

26
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:59,100
♫ Or... or is it meant to be? ♫

27
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:04,810
[My Uncanny Destiny]

28
00:02:09,620 --> 00:02:15,990
[My Uncanny Destiny: Episode 12]

29
00:02:15,990 --> 00:02:17,740
Zhi Lan.

30
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:20,660
- Zhi Lan, don't scare me.
- Zhi Lan.

31
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:22,020
Zhi Lan!

32
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:23,850
San Mei.

33
00:02:23,850 --> 00:02:26,630
- What happened to her?
- I don't know.

34
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:28,300
She wore the wedding dress, then she became like this.

35
00:02:28,300 --> 00:02:30,070
Call the imperial doctor, hurry.

36
00:02:30,070 --> 00:02:32,730
I'll go. I'll go.

37
00:02:32,730 --> 00:02:36,240
It's just a wedding dress. How come it became like this?

38
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:39,239
I remember. She seemed to get pricked by a needle on a button.

39
00:02:39,239 --> 00:02:40,829
Where?

40
00:02:40,829 --> 00:02:42,710
It seems to be here.

41
00:02:43,770 --> 00:02:46,340
This needle has poison on it.

42
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,960
Zhi Lan.

43
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,759
I-It was Princess Qi Meng who asked me to change the wedding dress.

44
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:57,479
I know nothing. I know nothing.

45
00:02:58,380 --> 00:03:01,580
I know nothing.

46
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:05,210
Second Oldest Sister.

47
00:03:05,210 --> 00:03:07,820
Zhi Lan.

48
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:11,760
I-I don't want to die yet.

49
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,909
You won't. You will be all right.

50
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:19,340
I want to return to Mu Xi

51
00:03:19,340 --> 00:03:23,990
to have a life belonging to Jin Zhi Lan.

52
00:03:23,990 --> 00:03:25,640
Okay.

53
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:31,560
I want to wear a real wedding dress once more.

54
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:35,700
You will. You will.

55
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,500
I'm so sleepy.

56
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:42,110
Don't be sleepy. The imperial doctor is on the way.

57
00:03:42,110 --> 00:03:46,150
Zhi Lan, don't be sleepy. Zhi Lan, don't fall asleep.

58
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,870
I must stay awake.

59
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,550
Zhi Lan.

60
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,160
Zhi Lan.

61
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:54,349
- Zhi Lan.
- Zhi Lan.

62
00:03:54,350 --> 00:03:56,239
- Second Oldest Sister.
- Zhi Lan.

63
00:03:56,239 --> 00:03:58,200
Second Oldest Sister.

64
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:02,260
- Zhi Lan.
- Second Oldest Sister.

65
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,779
- Second Oldest Sister.
- Zhi Lan.

66
00:04:03,779 --> 00:04:07,639
- Second Oldest Sister.
- Zhi Lan. Wake up, Zhi Lan.

67
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:16,130
I'll kill Qi Meng.

68
00:04:16,130 --> 00:04:19,139
Murder is my specialty. Leave it to me.

69
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:24,600
Let me kill her!

70
00:04:25,530 --> 00:04:29,260
Just one word from you, and the marriage will be no more.

71
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:31,920
I'll kill her for you.

72
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:36,500
This marriage must be done.

73
00:04:38,020 --> 00:04:40,740
Listen up, all of you.

74
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:43,590
Qi Meng is mine to kill,

75
00:04:43,590 --> 00:04:46,450
and no one else can do it.

76
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:02,340
She's so lucky.

77
00:05:02,340 --> 00:05:05,120
She can live a few more days.

78
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,480
Are you crazy?

79
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:15,049
I was away just two days, and you already stirred up a lot of trouble!

80
00:05:15,049 --> 00:05:19,300
I have repeatedly warned you against causing any unnecessary trouble.

81
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:21,950
You will irritate them by doing so!

82
00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:26,150
On the royal wedding night,

83
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:30,710
the whole Xuan Yue City will be ours.

84
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:35,700
I can kill whomever I want.

85
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:38,700
Even if I massacre all Xuan Yue City residents,

86
00:05:39,930 --> 00:05:41,840
what can you do to me?

87
00:05:41,840 --> 00:05:44,760
The "Ideal City Plan" we prepared for a long time,

88
00:05:44,760 --> 00:05:49,359
isn't it to take over Xuan Yue peacefully, then join forces with Tian Mu to unify Mu Xi,

89
00:05:49,359 --> 00:05:53,500
and ultimately, create an ideal city without war but prosperity for everyone?

90
00:05:53,500 --> 00:05:58,640
Now, it seems if you are the one to rule Xuan Yue, slaughter will only increase.

91
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:03,660
I will now inform officers and soldiers in the city to terminate this plan instantly.

92
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:14,260
You are verbose (gabby).

93
00:06:14,260 --> 00:06:20,020
No one can stop me from doing what I want.

94
00:06:38,770 --> 00:06:41,399
- Halt!
- What are you here for?

95
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:44,410
Sirs, His Majesty marries, yet you still work so hard.

96
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:48,120
Here, have some fruits and take a break. Here.

97
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:50,500
- Come on.
- Here.

98
00:06:56,740 --> 00:06:58,680
Hurry, hurry.

99
00:07:04,300 --> 00:07:06,300
[Double Happiness]

100
00:07:07,440 --> 00:07:11,820
"Heaven and Earth are light; the sun and moon are bright."

101
00:07:11,820 --> 00:07:15,560
"It has been 300 years since Xuan Yue City was built,"

102
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:18,700
"and it was passed down to Lord Xuan Ming,"

103
00:07:18,700 --> 00:07:22,190
"whose greatness and wisdom are worthy of his ancestors."

104
00:07:22,190 --> 00:07:25,290
"His morality joins Heaven and Earth to generate all."

105
00:07:25,290 --> 00:07:28,840
"His brightness coordinates the sun and moon to illuminate all."

106
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:31,920
"His decrees orderly unite with the four seasons."

107
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:36,430
"His merits attune with spirits and gods to decide good and bad fortune."

108
00:07:36,430 --> 00:07:39,190
"On this auspicious day and time,"

109
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:42,990
"he chooses a spouse and gets married."

110
00:07:42,990 --> 00:07:50,779
"They will live in harmony and revitalize Xuan Yue together to console our ancestors."

111
00:08:34,980 --> 00:08:39,210
San Mei, your clothes are stained with blood. Why didn't you wash them clean?

112
00:08:39,210 --> 00:08:41,209
It is inauspicious.

113
00:08:41,209 --> 00:08:45,150
We need to be clean on the big day.

114
00:08:45,150 --> 00:08:50,020
If you are clean doesn't depend on clothes, but on the person.

115
00:08:50,940 --> 00:08:53,300
If the person is too dirty,

116
00:08:53,300 --> 00:08:58,780
she should be skinned and washed thoroughly.

117
00:10:06,420 --> 00:10:08,200
You are so beautiful.

118
00:10:10,880 --> 00:10:13,890
The auspicious time has arrived!

119
00:10:13,890 --> 00:10:16,880
Bow to Heaven and Earth!

120
00:10:16,880 --> 00:10:18,530
Not so fast.

121
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:26,350
What qualification does she have to perform the wedding ceremony with me?

122
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:31,740
You've got a good point.

123
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:33,369
- Guards.
- Here.

124
00:10:33,369 --> 00:10:36,320
Send Princess Qi Meng away.

125
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:41,640
Liu Xuan Ming, are you stupid?

126
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:44,769
You don't marry me, the great princess of Tian Mu City, but her instead?

127
00:10:44,769 --> 00:10:49,220
So all the more reason for you to reflect on yourself.

128
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:53,360
I think you are the one who should reflect on yourself.

129
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:56,320
You could all have lived,

130
00:10:56,320 --> 00:10:58,120
but now,

131
00:10:59,060 --> 00:11:02,500
I'll show you what happens when you offend me!

132
00:11:02,500 --> 00:11:05,760
First, you used the royal wedding to make Xuan Yue City lively.

133
00:11:05,760 --> 00:11:09,869
Then you ordered Tian Mu soldiers to blend into the crowd and sneak into Xuan Yue City.

134
00:11:09,869 --> 00:11:14,360
So when I walked down the street that day, I felt something was off.

135
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:19,830
Those jugglers and sellers carrying poles didn't look like ordinary civilians at all.

136
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:22,360
You brought many war horses as dowry for no reason

137
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,840
and specially assigned your hostlers (stablemen) to them.

138
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:28,220
You wanted Xuan Yue's cavalry replaced with your own horses;

139
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:32,880
once the city riot started, your stablemen could control all the horses, right?

140
00:11:32,880 --> 00:11:36,080
You thought about everything.

141
00:11:37,070 --> 00:11:41,520
What you just said is right, but so what?

142
00:11:48,520 --> 00:11:54,350
What was sent to the sky just now was the signal that Tian Mu people took control of Xuan Yue City.

143
00:11:55,620 --> 00:12:00,400
You will all be prisoners in no time.

144
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:28,210
Since we already guessed your intention,

145
00:12:28,210 --> 00:12:31,040
how can we not prepare for it?

146
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:36,319
- Arrest them all!
- Arrest them all!

147
00:12:50,920 --> 00:12:53,309
- Take them down.
- Yes.

148
00:12:55,260 --> 00:12:56,830
You...

149
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:02,730
From the start, you never intended to unite with Xuan Yue through marriage.

150
00:13:02,730 --> 00:13:07,130
If I guessed it correctly, you planned to attack Xuan Yue City first,

151
00:13:07,130 --> 00:13:11,310
then use Xuan Yue City to attack Mu Xi City.

152
00:13:11,310 --> 00:13:14,310
To take down two cities with one ploy,

153
00:13:16,380 --> 00:13:18,800
what a good plan!

154
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:22,610
Don't be complacent; I am the princess of Tian Mu City.

155
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:25,070
Do you dare to kill me?

156
00:13:25,070 --> 00:13:31,070
I just received the news that your father has died.

157
00:13:31,070 --> 00:13:35,360
At this moment, your brothers are busy fighting for the throne.

158
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:40,250
Even if you die, I'm afraid they won't bother.

159
00:13:43,620 --> 00:13:48,230
- Your Highness.
- Is my father dead?

160
00:13:58,220 --> 00:14:03,420
Brother Xuan Ming, please forgive me for the sake that we grew up together.

161
00:14:03,420 --> 00:14:06,050
I was instructed by my father and sister.

162
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:09,570
I didn't want to kill people; I didn't.

163
00:14:09,570 --> 00:14:14,339
You changed your attitude so fast! Just now you said you would kill us all.

164
00:14:14,339 --> 00:14:18,150
- I said that just to scare you.
- What about my second oldest sister?

165
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:21,040
What a vicious woman you are.

166
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:24,490
That was all done by the maid, Qian Er; I didn't know about it!

167
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:28,500
It was not me. It was Her Highness. Her Highness told me to do it.

168
00:14:28,500 --> 00:14:31,450
Brother Xuan Ming. Brother Xuan Ming.

169
00:14:31,450 --> 00:14:35,590
You know me. When I was little,

170
00:14:35,590 --> 00:14:39,779
I got very sad when a bunny fell in water. I'm not such a person.

171
00:14:45,660 --> 00:14:51,070
Speaking of bunnies, I guess you don't know rabbits can swim.

172
00:14:51,810 --> 00:14:59,230
When I was little, I witnessed that you pressed the bunny I gave you into the water to drown it,

173
00:15:00,740 --> 00:15:03,450
then you sat there and wailed.

174
00:15:24,260 --> 00:15:29,369
Brother Xuan Ming, it was just a misunderstanding, just a misunderstanding, misunderstanding.

175
00:15:39,910 --> 00:15:43,890
San Mei, I'm begging you. Please save me.

176
00:15:43,890 --> 00:15:46,819
Save me. San Mei.

177
00:15:56,570 --> 00:16:01,630
Prepare the best war horse in Tian Mu City for me at once. Quick!

178
00:16:01,630 --> 00:16:03,240
Prepare the horse!

179
00:16:03,240 --> 00:16:04,760
Move.

180
00:16:07,720 --> 00:16:11,950
Don't come any closer, or I'll kill her.

181
00:16:12,610 --> 00:16:14,600
Stay back!

182
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:19,890
- Oldest Sister.
- With San Mei's ability,

183
00:16:19,890 --> 00:16:22,049
- Move aside.
- Qi Meng can't hurt her.

184
00:16:22,049 --> 00:16:24,840
Then why did my oldest sister let herself be kidnapped?

185
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:27,760
She wants to end this with her alone.

186
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:29,280
Go!

187
00:16:31,210 --> 00:16:32,690
Go.

188
00:16:33,470 --> 00:16:37,949
Don't be afraid. You are the one with the knife. I can't hurt you.

189
00:16:40,510 --> 00:16:42,840
Guan San Mei.

190
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:45,460
I ended up like this all because of you.

191
00:16:45,460 --> 00:16:48,120
You are so funny.

192
00:16:48,120 --> 00:16:50,860
Obviously, you harmed people first,

193
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:53,220
but now, you blame others instead.

194
00:16:53,220 --> 00:16:56,160
Is it true that for people like you,

195
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:59,110
other people's lives are as cheap as grass?

196
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:01,900
Don't talk so much rubbish.

197
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:04,000
I'll kill you!

198
00:17:07,860 --> 00:17:09,260
Giddy-up (faster)!

199
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:23,460
Giddy-up!

200
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:27,579
His Majesty ordered no one can leave the city.

201
00:17:33,850 --> 00:17:35,280
Giddy-up!

202
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,720
Giddy-up!

203
00:17:57,620 --> 00:18:02,730
This shot is for Ke Qian Yue.

204
00:18:02,730 --> 00:18:08,480
You used her to not only harm me but her as well.

205
00:18:14,610 --> 00:18:18,450
This shot is for Liu Xuan Ming.

206
00:18:18,450 --> 00:18:20,860
How dare you hit on my man?

207
00:18:20,860 --> 00:18:25,049
San Mei, I'm begging you. Please don't kill me.

208
00:18:29,070 --> 00:18:34,440
Don't you fear my sister will come after you for treating me like this?

209
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:39,630
This shot is for Zhi Lan.

210
00:18:51,510 --> 00:18:56,080
Guan San Mei. I don't believe you dare to kill me.

211
00:18:56,080 --> 00:18:58,120
My sister is quite intimidating.

212
00:18:58,120 --> 00:19:03,400
She will torture you until you wish you can die, but you can't.

213
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:05,750
I'll wait.

214
00:19:08,020 --> 00:19:11,020
But I also have a secret to tell you.

215
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:14,510
I...

216
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:18,820
am not Guan San Mei.

217
00:19:20,780 --> 00:19:22,690
I am...

218
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:27,520
the lord of Mu Xi,

219
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:35,580
Ye... Zhao... Nan.

220
00:20:01,850 --> 00:20:10,290
[Tomb of My Dead Sister, Jin Zhi Lan]

221
00:20:17,300 --> 00:20:22,630
If I had insisted on opposing this marriage,

222
00:20:25,130 --> 00:20:28,310
perhaps you wouldn't have died.

223
00:20:33,550 --> 00:20:37,740
[Tomb of My Dead Sister, Jin Zhi Lan]

224
00:20:37,740 --> 00:20:41,760
We share both weal and woe.

225
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:44,840
We weren't born on the same day,

226
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:48,610
- but we wish to d–
- Wait a minute.

227
00:20:49,480 --> 00:20:52,760
It's too scary to die together.

228
00:20:52,760 --> 00:20:57,149
It's hard to bury us all. We need to have a sequence.

229
00:20:57,149 --> 00:20:59,240
Then who will die first?

230
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,800
I'll be the first.

231
00:21:03,950 --> 00:21:06,560
Why are you fighting for this?

232
00:21:07,840 --> 00:21:09,720
Let fate decide.

233
00:21:21,370 --> 00:21:24,999
You fool. What does this have to do with you?

234
00:21:25,900 --> 00:21:28,180
You have tried your best.

235
00:21:28,180 --> 00:21:32,770
You worked hard to make the people of Mu Xi City happy.

236
00:21:33,690 --> 00:21:38,950
It isn't easy for you to fight alone against corrupt, outdated concepts in the first place.

237
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:41,980
The long road is dangerous, but you will reach it; keep going.

238
00:21:41,980 --> 00:21:45,430
Persevere, then a bright future is worth it.

239
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:50,780
The road ahead will be more difficult; you must persevere

240
00:21:50,780 --> 00:21:52,990
and never give up.

241
00:22:17,340 --> 00:22:21,400
[General's Manor]

242
00:22:27,420 --> 00:22:29,310
Jin Ting.

243
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:31,690
Brother, I'm going to learn to dance.

244
00:22:31,690 --> 00:22:33,120
"Dance"?

245
00:22:33,120 --> 00:22:37,060
How absurd! As a man, how can you learn something so feminine?

246
00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:39,550
Come here and practice with me.

247
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:42,799
His Majesty decreed men's jobs are for women, and women's jobs are for men.

248
00:22:42,799 --> 00:22:46,179
- No distinction is between superiority and inferiority.
- Don't mention His Majesty!

249
00:22:46,179 --> 00:22:49,770
Your sister is still missing; aren't you worried about her?

250
00:22:49,770 --> 00:22:54,150
Thus, I will ask all my dancing friends to seek news of my sister everywhere.

251
00:22:54,150 --> 00:22:56,010
I'm leaving.

252
00:22:58,370 --> 00:23:00,650
