275
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:24,110
Ye Zhao Nan will surely agree to an alliance.

276
00:24:24,110 --> 00:24:30,340
"Today, our benevolent lord is willing to make peace with Mu Xi and cease war forever."

277
00:24:30,340 --> 00:24:35,530
"He hereby appoints Guan San Mei as Xuan Yue's envoy"

278
00:24:35,530 --> 00:24:39,390
"to Mu Xi City for peace talks."

279
00:24:39,390 --> 00:24:44,569
I will carry out my mission and succeed in achieving peace talks.

280
00:24:46,140 --> 00:24:50,500
All the people in the world are blessed by our benevolent His Majesty.

281
00:24:50,500 --> 00:24:55,720
It's Xuan Yue's fortune and blessing to have you.

282
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:59,820
