284
00:25:04,260 --> 00:25:07,600
The unjust person is doomed to destruction.

285
00:25:07,600 --> 00:25:10,499
I must go to Mu Xi City for peace talks, and I need your help.

286
00:25:10,499 --> 00:25:13,020
Join me on my journey to Mu Xi City.

