291
00:25:28,990 --> 00:25:32,859
My belief is to free civilians from wars, starvation, poverty,

292
00:25:32,859 --> 00:25:35,440
eliminate lines of superiority and inferiority,

293
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:41,630
and achieve great unity where people prosper together.

294
00:25:41,630 --> 00:25:45,170
A world of great unity where people prosper together?

295
00:25:45,170 --> 00:25:49,230
The peace talks between Xuan Yue and Mu Xi are the first step.

296
00:25:49,230 --> 00:25:55,230
